Qubes Management
================

- Install salt via template +salt
- Install salt via dom0
  - qvm-run copy
  - qvm-execute to install
  - qvm hightstate-test
  - qvm get-report
  - send to SaltVM

Salt Modules
============
- qvm-run
- start, stop, create (like qubes manager)
- qubes-dom0-update in place of yum update


